lead_paragraph: Holders Spain may have been inferior in a 2-0 defeat by Italy in the last 16 at Euro 2016 on Monday but their exit did not mark the end of an era and they have a bright future, said coach Vicente Del Bosque

headline.print_headline: Spain Have Bright Future Despite Euro Defeat-Del Bosque
